    "z": "flow27",
    "name": "PX4: stream FIRST, then switch to OFFBOARD",
    "info": "PX4 will not enter OFFBOARD unless setpoints are already streaming at >= ~2 Hz, and it falls out of OFFBOARD if the stream stalls. Step 1 therefore starts the stream before step 2 changes the mode. ArduPilot GUIDED accepts discrete targets without a stream, but the same ordering is harmless there.",
